      "text": "បន្ទាប់​មក​វា​ឃើញ​ឆ្កែ​កំពុង​អង្គុយ​មើល​វា។"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f0f8fcbe0-3021-4f67-ac1c-5e1b6c304e87%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a7+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%a2%e1%9f%82%e1%9e%9c%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%2fimage3.png",
      "text": "វាលោតចុះពីលើដើមឈើហើយរត់ទៅ។\nបន្ទាប់មក៖ ឆ្កែដេញតាមឆ្មាជិតទាន់។"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f0f8fcbe0-3021-4f67-ac1c-5e1b6c304e87%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a7+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%a2%e1%9f%82%e1%9e%9c%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%2fimage4.png",
      "text": "មកដល់ផ្ទះមួយឆ្មារត់លោតឡើងដំបូលផ្ទះ។"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f0f8fcbe0-3021-4f67-ac1c-5e1b6c304e87%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a7+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%a2%e1%9f%82%e1%9e%9c%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%2fimage5.png",
      "text": "បន្ទាប់មកឆ្កែសួរថា៖ “ហេតុអ្វីបានជាឯងរត់? ឯងខ្លាចខ្ញុំឬ?”"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f0f8fcbe0-3021-4f67-ac1c-5e1b6c304e87%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a7+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%a2%e1%9f%82%e1%9e%9c%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%2fimage6.png",
      "text": "ឆ្មាឆ្លើយថា៖ “ខ្ញុំមិនខ្លាចឯងទេ”។"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f0f8fcbe0-3021-4f67-ac1c-5e1b6c304e87%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a7+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%a2%e1%9f%82%e1%9e%9c%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%2fimage8.png",
      "text": "បន្ទាប់មកឆ្មាក៏ចុះមកជួបនិងឆ្កែ ហើយនិយាយថា៖ “ខ្ញុំរត់ល្បងកំលាំងទេតើ”។ “ឆ្កែឆ្លើយថា៖ “មែនឬ?”"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f0f8fcbe0-3021-4f67-ac1c-5e1b6c304e87%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a7+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%a2%e1%9f%82%e1%9e%9c%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%2fimage9.png",
      "text": "ឆ្មានិយាយថា៖ “អើ! ខ្ញុំធាត់ណាស់ ចឹងបានខ្ញុំរត់”។"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f0f8fcbe0-3021-4f67-ac1c-5e1b6c304e87%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a7+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%a2%e1%9f%82%e1%9e%9c%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%2fimage10.png",
      "text": "តើឯងទៅរកកណ្ដុរជាមួយខ្ញុំទេ? ឆ្កែឆ្លើយ៖ តោះ! ទៅចឹង!"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f0f8fcbe0-3021-4f67-ac1c-5e1b6c304e87%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a7+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%a2%e1%9f%82%e1%9e%9c%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%2fimage11.png",
      "text": "ពួកវាឃើញកណ្ដុរពីរ តែឆ្មាចង់ខាំកណ្ដុរនោះ។ ឃើញដូច្នេះឆ្កែនឹកអាណិតកណ្ដុរជាខ្លាំង ក៏និយាយជាមួយឆ្មាថា៖ “មើលកណ្ដុរទៅ វាឃ្លានខ្លាំងណាស់”។"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f0f8fcbe0-3021-4f67-ac1c-5e1b6c304e87%2f%e1%9f%a1%e1%9f%a7+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%a2%e1%9f%82%e1%9e%9c%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%8a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%86%e1%9f%9d%2fimage12.png",
      "text": "បន្ទាប់មកឆ្មានិងឆ្កែបបួលកណ្ដុរទៅផ្ទះដាំបាយធ្វើសម្លរហូប៕"
    }
